{"tid":1335243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［7.21.見］藍田有愛！","createTime":"2019-07-20T12:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T13:05:51.000Z","uid":16355,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9771c326c7bcd54c35bed7888b65329a8c31837c","tid":1335243,"uid":16355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:16:21.000Z","msg":"岩岩係藍田B出口，貼連儂牆個陣，個痴線藍絲屌。<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位街坊幫手出口、拍片。<br />\n<br />\n聽日7月21日見！<br />\n<br />\n特此附上廢老圖乙張。就係黑衫，藍牛仔褲！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J459GUS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ459GUS.png&h=3ccace5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bac6bcd333fddd919fbe813776ee1852c28c2244","tid":1335243,"uid":113797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f20f72836d6599f94639cb94978226e934e64d63","tid":1335243,"uid":86485,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftNLZHc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftNLZHc.jpg&h=cbf49955&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點可以漏咗隔離藍衫女士"},{"pid":"1b2384d2ae80888530a7829b7376e0b13205fcf1","tid":1335243,"uid":16355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"多謝現場各位街坊！<br />\n深藍重災區都要救！"},{"pid":"c086af4c16963ed3d70eb3c0c84354c0c5b6caff","tid":1335243,"uid":52155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:31:28.000Z","msg":"又嚟一條藍屍，藍田真係重災區"},{"pid":"047df5f914f40f78ac37ede12a353844ae621b63","tid":1335243,"uid":86485,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:45:49.000Z","msg":"講返啱先發生咩事先：<br />\n一開頭嚟到就見到男廢物手拎撕咗落嚟嘅紙，有個伯伯同有位太太睇唔過眼佢蝦後生仔，又驚佢打仲痴緊牆嘅兄弟，同佢理論。好多謝佢地，好彩有佢地！伯伯屌呢啲廢物仲要忍受廢物嘅口臭，辛苦曬！<br />\n<br />\n然後男廢物講講下有女廢物加入，佢地話好多人圍住一個警察打，要拉曬佢地喎！然後男廢物走去繼續撕紙，啱啱好有位兄弟行過見到即刻大聲喝罵：「你做乜嘢啊！」可能呢位兄弟極大聲屌佢嘅原故，打咗支強心針比其他兄弟姊妹一齊屌。<br />\n<br />\n最後大家以「中國人咁你點解唔返大陸住啊？」呢條問題問到兩件廢物口啞啞，成功擊退！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然有兄弟話過僆儂牆唔使守，撕一貼百，但上天賜予我地個咁好嘅機會去屌鳩啲廢物，咁都冇理由唔屌嫁係咪先？<br />\n<br />\n啱先真係各有各做，痴牆嘅痴牆，拍片嘅拍片，屌嘅就大大力屌，企係到維護嘅繼續維護，以大比數勝出！覺得攰嘅今晚返去抖，總之聽日見啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3dbddec104deb30a311e4e914947dd47dcf728d","tid":1335243,"uid":261892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:51:44.000Z","msg":"以前一到雙十節成個藍田掛滿 青天白日滿地紅旗， 超級壯觀！ <br />\n真係想唔到回歸後 ，就變曬勁共勁共。"},{"pid":"ece5ee3f2b0956b9ca97b313505e0286e13f69dc","tid":1335243,"uid":86485,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"以免有咩誤會，放大啲比大家睇清楚，認撚住佢先。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ceRVvn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ceRVvn.png&h=6164d1f0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VetbVvq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVetbVvq.png&h=9c8b1d8c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nzsTpoQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnzsTpoQ.png&h=9862b9da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非伯伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8eqZXL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8eqZXL.png&h=dd2d7264&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n敗走圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8yQ9Hap.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8yQ9Hap.jpg&h=6e8cb8ef&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}